## 23. File Reading

```java
import java.io.File;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class FileReading {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        try {

            File file =
                    new File("output.txt");

            Scanner reader =
                    new Scanner(file);

            while(reader.hasNextLine()) {

                System.out.println(
                        reader.nextLine()
                );
            }

            reader.close();

        }
        catch(Exception e) {

            System.out.println(
                    "File not found."
            );
        }
    }
}
```

