## 26. Thread Creation

```java
class MyThread extends Thread {

    private String message;

    MyThread(String message) {
        this.message = message;
    }

    public void run() {

        for(int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {

            System.out.println(
                    message + " " + i
            );
        }
    }
}

public class ThreadExample {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        MyThread t1 =
                new MyThread("Thread A");

        MyThread t2 =
                new MyThread("Thread B");

        t1.start();
        t2.start();
    }
}
```

