## 29. Records (Java 16+)

```java
import java.util.List;

record Person(
        String name,
        int age
) {}

public class RecordExample {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        Person p1 =
                new Person("Falak",21);

        Person p2 =
                new Person("Rahul",17);

        System.out.println(p1);
        System.out.println(p2);

        List<Person> people =
                List.of(p1,p2);

        people.stream()
              .filter(
                    p -> p.age() >= 18
              )
              .forEach(System.out::println);
    }
}
```

